<script>
import { Pie } from "vue-chartjs"

export default {
  extends: Pie,
  mounted() {
    fetch("http://localhost:3000/infos/usersByGender")
      .then((res) => {
        return res.json()
      })
      .then((response) => {
        console.log(response)
        let labelsParam = []
        let datasetsParam = [{ data: [] }]

        response.data.totalUsersByGender.forEach((element) => {
          labelsParam.push(element.VwGeneralRegisters_gender)
          datasetsParam[0].data.push(element.TotalByGender)
        })
        datasetsParam[0].label = "Total de Usu√°rios"
        datasetsParam[0].backgroundColor = [
          "rgb(54, 162, 235)",
          "rgb(255, 99, 132)",
          "rgb(255, 205, 86)",
        ]

        this.renderChart(
          {
            labels: labelsParam,
            datasets: datasetsParam,
          },
          {
            responsive: true,
            maintainAspectRatio: false,
          }
        )

        // this.renderChart(

}
</script>
